Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,MYST AND KILL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you want with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Popp is dead,\Nwe have no way of defeating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see just how central\Nthat boy was to your group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NKill respected him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He said such people can become\Nthe heart and soul of their team,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so they should be gotten rid of first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,His valiant efforts\Nare deserving of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He even forced me to use the Phoenix Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Phoenix Wing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a high-speed palm strike\Nthat reflects any spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Medoroa is an exception to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have survived that attack\Nwithout using this forbidden skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Phoenix... The immortal bird...\NThat means...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see! Then Mystban is Ban's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got it!\NI know Mystban's true identity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if I'm right, it makes sense\Nthat he's this powerful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercy is an insult. Kill me quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember this,\NMaster Dai will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The all-important Dai still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it quick for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can await Dai in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times\NDai grows in power,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he can never kill Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai can't kill Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the real Ban...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the real Dark King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all seen him together with\Nthe Dark King numerous times yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it would be you, Hyunckel,\Nto be the first to realize the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Mystban revealed his face,\NI sensed a familiar presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was none other than\NDark King Ban's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,While his voice may be youthful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,his mannerisms and fighting style\Nall line up with Ban's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect the reason Mystban\Nwas forced to keep silent for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,was because if someone\Nfamiliar with Ban heard his voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they might realize the similarities\Nbetween the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the Dark King can't be silent,\Nthen the shadow must.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But that shadow was really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just say that\Nyou're mostly correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can figure out the rest\Nafter you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on. He's said that much.\NWhy not tell us the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear more about who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find his hand over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be! Please! No more, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tragedy upon tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, Kill,\Nwhat did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mean by what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To say something as absurd as\Nwanting to know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Over these centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you've seen me fight\Nrevealed like this a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said to you then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't bother asking."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Not even you will be spared if\Nyou knew the true meaning of this face."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am no exception to that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why, when I tried\Nto reveal this face before,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you threatened to kill me, didn't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you go forgetting either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be obligated to help the Dark King,\Nbut I'm not duty-bound to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the Dark Army,\Nonly you are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You are nearly equal\Nto Dark King Ban himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I still remember\Nthe day you first appeared before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So which... is King Ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban... is what you can call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you are of his...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a messenger from one you know well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My specialty is assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have dressed this way\Nspecifically for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As a gesture of friendship from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been sent as an aide\Nto help you in your plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As an aide...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And if my plans should happen to fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you will immediately attempt\Nto assassinate me, will you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A watchdog over my plan\Nto destroy the Surface World.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In other word, a coded name\Nmeaning "Eliminate Ban."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly the god of the Underworld.\NYou are very gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This one, like yourself,\Nis a powerful being of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He is my right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was immediately impressed by you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To appear before the Dark King\Nyet remain so calm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your brazen attitude was quite impressive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over the next few centuries,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,while our personalities were opposite,\Nwe got along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it turns out\NI'd been lied to this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You were never truly\Na servant of Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You merely worked with him\Nunder orders from your master.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'm the real Ban,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it would mean you've been\Nhelping someone completely different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would mean\Nour strange friendship was also false.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no mistake in your aid to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and neither is there to our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you just reveal\Nyour secret to us here, Mystban?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not the Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The official name of Mystban\Nwas given to me after Kill arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't call me Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He calls me by my old name of Myst!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Reveal yourself, faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. That was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I overlooked a rudimentary thing\Nlike what you call each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A Morph spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the Transformation Spell Morph,\Nhe was pretending to be Kilban!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to join you, but Hyunckel was\Nin the middle of solving the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd take Kilban's form\Nand have the secret revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, he said it himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he may be obligated to help the Dark King,\Nbut he isn't duty-bound to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kill? What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing as I'm here, there only one answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reaper... was the one who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.48,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}MEDOROA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.48,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,REAPER FLUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reaper... was the one who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dai defeats him then that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be obligated to help him,\Nbut I'm not duty-bound to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like Myst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear\Njust how you're not like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just his glove?! And it's full of sand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that this surprised even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is magic sand that I concocted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I uses Lunar Rurabloom\Nmaking it a marker against enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use the Lilirura spell to catch up\Nto where this is applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it works even if\Na dimension is closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd realize if I threw it on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so I snuck some in my glove\Nand grabbed your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may have intended to slice my wrist,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I retracted my hand in that instant,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and successfully got my glove\Nand the sand back to this dimension.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the last gamble I could make\Nwhen grabbed by the Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your cheap parlour tricks\Nthat surprise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why are you still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Judge's Megante!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only call it a rare miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be the only human who's suffered\Na Megante spell twice in their lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I've survived, all that remains\Nis to use what life I have against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Kilban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Wave Strike!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He should have sustained heavy damage!\NAnd yet he remains so strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been called the Reaper,\Nbut for the first time, I'm scared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've used all the traps I can against him,\Nso how is he still alive?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've used all your Phantom Razors,\Nand your Judge is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you've prepared any other traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it's really over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can survive even with my limbs\Nor even my torso severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm neither mad nor suicidal,\Nso any concern is unnecessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that sphere?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One arm should be enough\Nto finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I never like to harm myself, so to make me\Nuse this is quite a feat, Aban, the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one of the few men\NKing Ban feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I offer a final attack worthy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Incinerating Inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an intense fireball!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My blood is the same composition\Nas Underworld magma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Once lit, it becomes\Na blaze of scorching heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's his true ace in the hole!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I doubt it can be stopped or dodged.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case,\NI'll use my greatest attack against it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Strash, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly a threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't compare with this attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Says the man fighting seriously\Nfor the first time in his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow insult!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I control the life and death of all!\NI am the god of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful! I was right\Nto use this attack to finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you should\Nstick to doing things you're good at!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could he survive\Nmy Incinerating Inferno?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra's ashes\Nfrom when he died in my arms...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did they protect me from the Megante\Nand Incinerating Inferno?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra, did you protect me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra saved me through such a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he really did despise\Nwhat you did, Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How could something as nebulous\Nas a miracle defeat me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra's body was made of Superior Being\Ncells that could emit Dark Fire Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They remained as ashes,\Nshielding you from heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. That's the only explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A miracle... A miracle could never...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I used Aban Strash,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the residual blaze around me\Ncaught on to his body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It ignited the magma blood\Nthat flows in his veins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! This is very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&} {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadaruko!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&} {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadain!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! Not for me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'm begging you! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban's going to be reduced to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him not to be bad anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. I think I am, Piroro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should thank Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't fully trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never encountered an enemy\Nso cruel and lacking of merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I insist you accept these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed to enjoy my Phantom Razors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With Piroro, I can restock my blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you're aware,\Nonly I know where these 13 blades are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the tables have turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was 100% certain this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I already laid a trap for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to keep\Nthe life that I spared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,then don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lying! It has to be a bluff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You? Laid a trap? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A Phantom Razor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one from\Nthe other dimension that was stuck in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It came back to this dimension with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the 14th invisible blade\Nto the 13 you released.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you didn't know where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You planted it when you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I got sloppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. He can't be healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even immortal, no living creature\Ncan survive without its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The loser loses their head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cruel, but those were his rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,was defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That little familiar of his\Ncan't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban, the Reaper is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, thanks to what you've said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your real identity, Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as Ban,\Nthe Dark King's greatest secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having won against Kilban, Aban sees\Nthrough the Dark King's greatest secret,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and begins revealing it to everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Dai blew Ban away\Nwith his Doru Aura, but dark clouds gather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dots of Ban's mystery connect,\Nand rise as the greatest threat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:23:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:23:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Ban's Truth"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:23:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
